  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Establishes the New York native plants program to conserve, promote, and enhance the native ecology of New York state by encouraging the use of native plants and ecological-friendly methods and materials on state and local land."
    }
